TITLE: Determining Front Face of 3D Cube Using Matrix Inversion in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: A function that determines if a face of a 3D cube is currently facing forward by checking the sign of the z-scale of the inverted transformation matrix. It handles cases where the matrix might not be invertible.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/skia/blob/main/site/docs/user/modules/canvaskit.md#2025-04-08_snippet_9

