TITLE: Creating Picture Recording Canvas
DESCRIPTION: Creates a canvas for recording drawing commands into an SkPicture. Uses SkPictureRecorder to capture and serialize drawing commands.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/skia/blob/main/site/docs/user/api/skcanvas_creation.md#2025-04-08_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: C++
CODE:
```
#include "include/core/SkPictureRecorder.h"
#include "include/core/SkPicture.h"
#include "include/core/SkStream.h"
void picture(int width, int height,
             void (*draw)(SkCanvas*),
             const char* path) {
    SkPictureRecorder recorder;
    SkCanvas* recordingCanvas = recorder.beginRecording(SkIntToScalar(width),
                                                        SkIntToScalar(height));
    draw(recordingCanvas);
    sk_sp<SkPicture> picture = recorder.finishRecordingAsPicture();
    SkFILEWStream skpStream(path);
    picture->serialize(&skpStream);
}
```

