TITLE: Star Path Generation Function
DESCRIPTION: Creates a star-shaped path using CanvasKit Path API with configurable position and radius parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/skia/blob/main/site/docs/user/modules/canvaskit.md#2025-04-08_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
function starPath(CanvasKit, X=128, Y=128, R=116) {
  let p = new CanvasKit.Path();
  p.moveTo(X + R, Y);
  for (let i = 1; i < 8; i++) {
    let a = 2.6927937 * i;
    p.lineTo(X + R * Math.cos(a), Y + R * Math.sin(a));
  }
  return p;
}
```

