TITLE: Configuring ChromeOS ARM Build
DESCRIPTION: GN configuration for cross-compiling Skia for ARM ChromeOS devices with specific compiler flags and paths.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/skia/blob/main/site/docs/user/build.md#2025-04-08_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
#ARM
cc= "/opt/clang/bin/clang"
cxx = "/opt/clang/bin/clang++"

extra_asmflags = [
    "--target=armv7a-linux-gnueabihf",
    "--sysroot=/opt/armhf_sysroot/",
    "-march=armv7-a",
    "-mfpu=neon",
